<%- include("template/header") %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/guides.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/background.css">

    <!-- <div class="container-fluid">
        <span class="mx-auto">Feynman Technique</span>
    </div> -->

    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-white" style="display: inline-block;">
            <h4 class="text-center" style="margin: 10px;">
                Feynman Technique
            </h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>


    <div class="guide-section">
        <h2>Summary</h2>
        <p>
            The Feynman Technique is a powerful study method developed by Nobel Prize-winning physicist Richard Feynman.
            It involves breaking down complex topics into simple, understandable concepts and explaining them as if
            teaching a child. This technique helps deepen understanding and uncover knowledge gaps.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="guideCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <div class="guide-section">
                    <h2>Step 1</h2>
                    <p>Choose a Topic: Select the topic you want to learn or understand better.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="guide-section">
                    <h2>Step 2</h2>
                    <p>Explain the Topic: Write down everything you know about the topic as if you were teaching it to a
                        child or someone unfamiliar with the subject.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="guide-section">
                    <h2>Step 3</h2>
                    <p>Identify Gaps: Review your explanation and identify areas where your understanding is lacking or
                        unclear.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="guide-section">
                    <h2>Step 4</h2>
                    <p>Review and Simplify: Go back to your study materials to fill in the gaps, then simplify and
                        clarify your explanation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
                aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="3" aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-3">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">Prev</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">Next</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("template/footer") %>